casebody.data:
No. 235,

Mise.

Williams v. Illinois. Petitioner pro se. Ivan A. Elliott, Attorney General of Illinois, and William C. Wines, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent. Per Curiam:

The petition for writ of certiorari is granted. The judgment is vacated and the case is remanded to the Illinois Supreme Court for further proceedings. Jennings v. Illinois, 342 U. S. 104.
